         </div>\n 990 | \n 991 |                   <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 flex flex-col items-end text-right min-w-[170px] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n 992 |                     <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">IMPLEMENTATION HORIZON</span>\n 993 |                     <span className=\"text-base font-bold text-white font-mono print:text-black\">{pData.weeks} WEEKS</span>\n 994 |                     <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] mt-0.5 uppercase font-bold\">{pData.budgetLabel}</span>\n 995 |                   </div>\n 996 |                 </div>\n 997 | \n 998 |                 <div className=\"space-y-12 print:space-y-10 text-left\">\n 999 |                   {/* SECTION 1: EXECUTIVE SUMMARY */}\n1000 |                   <div id=\"executive-summary\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1001 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1002 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION I</span>\n1003 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">📄 Executive Summary</h2>\n1004 |                     </div>\n1005 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85\">\n1006 |                       <p>\n1007 |                         GFF AI recommends deploying a dedicated <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.engagementPathObj.label}</strong> architecture inside the single-tenant VPC perimeter for <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.org}</strong>. Operating inside the <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.industryLabel}</strong> vertical, GFF AI will deploy a dedicated single-tenant enclave designed to resolve the primary challenge: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.challengeLabel}</strong>.\n1008 |                       </p>\n1009 |                       <p>\n1010 |                         Over an implementation lifecycle of <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.weeks} Weeks</strong>, GFF will establish isolated secure pipelines under the guidance of key stakeholders (<strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.stakeholdersLabel}</strong>), delivering sovereign capabilities like:\n1011 |                       </p>\n1012 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 mt-4\">\n1013 |                         {pData.selectedOutcomeLabels.map((outcome, idx) => (\n1014 |                           <div key={idx} className=\"p-3 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] print:bg-black/5 print:border-black/10 flex items-center gap-2\">\n1015 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-mono text-[10px]\">✓</span>\n1016 |                             <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/80 print:text-black\">{outcome}</span>\n1017 |                           </div>\n1018 |                         ))}\n1019 |                       </div>\n1020 |                     </div>\n1021 |                   </div>\n1022 | \n1023 |                   {/* SECTION 2: CHALLENGE STATEMENT */}\n1024 |                   <div id=\"challenge-statement\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1025 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1026 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION II</span>\n1027 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">⚠️ Challenge Statement</h2>\n1028 |                     </div>\n1029 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1030 |                       <p>\n1031 |                         For a <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.companySizeLabel}</strong> operation, legacy or third-party cloud-hosted AI APIs introduce severe compliance risks and telemetry leaks. Private company IP can be used for public third-party model tuning. The primary bottleneck identified in this intake session is:\n1032 |                       </p>\n1033 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/10 bg-red-500/[0.02] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n1034 |                         <div className=\"flex gap-2 items-start\">\n1035 |                           <span className=\"text-red-400 mt-0.5\">⚠️</span>\n1036 |                           <div>\n1037 |                             <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-400 print:text-black uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">PRIORITY FRICTION DETECTED</h4>\n1038 |                             <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/80 print:text-black mt-1 leading-relaxed\">\n1039 |                               \"{pData.challengeLabel}\" is trapping valuable context inside isolated legacy silos, while exposing telemetry interfaces. This operational latency blocks prompt-chain efficiency and increases licensing costs.\n1040 |                             </p>\n1041 |                           </div>\n1042 |                         </div>\n1043 |                       </div>\n1044 |                     </div>\n1045 |                   </div>\n1046 | \n1047 |                   {/* SECTION 3: RECOMMENDED GFF PATH */}\n1048 |                   <div id=\"recommended-gff-path\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1049 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1050 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION III</span>\n1051 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">🚀 Recommended GFF Path</h2>\n1052 |                     </div>\n1053 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1054 |                       <p>\n1055 |                         GFF AI recommends the <strong className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-extrabold\">{pData.engagementPathObj.label}</strong> engagement path (Model: <span className=\"font-mono text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 print:bg-black/5 print:text-black text-white\">{pData.engagementPathObj.badge}</span>) to deliver secure, industrialized cognitive capabilities within your environment:\n1056 |                       </p>\n1057 |                       \n1058 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] print:bg-black/5 print:border-black/10 space-y-3\">\n1059 |                         <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n1060 |                           <span>SOVEREIGN ACTIVE DEPLOYMENT ARCHITECTURE</span>\n1061 |                           <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">VPC PERIMETER STAGED</span>\n1062 |                         </div>\n1063 |                         \n1064 |                         {/* Premium Topology map inline */}\n1065 |                         <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 py-3\">\n1066 |                           <div className=\"flex-1 w-full p-2.5 rounded border border-white/5 bg-black/40 text-center print:border-black/15\">\n1067 |                             <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/40 block mb-0.5\">LOCAL INGEST</span>\n1068 |                             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold text-white uppercase print:text-black\">{pData.industryLabel} Context</span>\n1069 |                           </div>\n1070 |                           <div className=\"text-[#009DFF] text-xs font-mono hidden md:block select-none\">▶▶</div>\n1071 |                           <div className=\"flex-1 w-full p-3 rounded border border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-center shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,157,255,0.05)] print:border-black/15\">\n1072 |                             <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] block mb-0.5\">VPC ENCLAVE</span>\n1073 |                             <span className=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white uppercase print:text-black\">{pData.engagementPathObj.badge} NODE</span>\n1074 |                           </div>\n1075 |                           <div className=\"text-[#00FF9D] text-xs font-mono hidden md:block select-none\">▶▶</div>\n1076 |                           <div className=\"flex-1 w-full p-2.5 rounded border border-[#00FF9D]/30 bg-[#00FF9D]/5 text-center shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,255,157,0.05)] print:border-black/15\">\n1077 |                             <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] block mb-0.5\">COMPLIANCE EDGE</span>\n1078 |                             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold text-white uppercase print:text-black\">ZERO RETENTION</span>\n1079 |                           </div>\n1080 |                         </div>\n1081 |                         <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-snug font-mono print:text-black/60\">\n1082 |                           Workloads are deployed completely within single-tenant VPC boundaries in <strong>{pData.geographyLabel}</strong>. Memory arrays clear prompt logs instantly.\n1083 |                         </p>\n1084 |                       </div>\n1085 |                     </div>\n1086 |                   </div>\n1087 | \n1088 |                   {/* SECTION 4: PROPOSED WORKSTREAMS */}\n1089 |                   <div id=\"proposed-workstreams\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1090 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1091 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION IV</span>\n1092 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">🗺️ Proposed Workstreams</h2>\n1093 |                     </div>\n1094 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1095 |                       <p>\n1096 |                         The technical integration of your sovereign AI nodes is divided into four distinct phases spanning the <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.weeks} Weeks</strong> schedule:\n1097 |                       </p>\n1098 |                       \n1099 |                       <div className=\"relative pl-6 border-l border-white/5 space-y-6 print:border-black/10\">\n1100 |                         <div className=\"relative text-left\">\n1101 |                           <span className=\"absolute -left-[29px] top-0.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center text-[7px] font-bold text-black font-mono\">A</span>\n1102 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono\">Phase A: Hardened Perimeter Setup <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-normal ml-2\">(Weeks 1 - {pData.p1})</span></h4>\n1103 |                           <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 mt-1 leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n1104 |                             Configure single-tenant geographic VPC rules inside {pData.geographyLabel}, stand up secure isolated container layers, and test zero-retention logging firewalls.\n1105 |                           </p>\n1106 |                         </div>\n1107 |                         <div className=\"relative text-left\">\n1108 |                           <span className=\"absolute -left-[29px] top-0.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center text-[7px] font-bold text-black font-mono\">B</span>\n1109 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono\">Phase B: Pipeline Core Integration <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-normal ml-2\">(Weeks {pData.p1 + 1} - {pData.p1 + pData.p2})</span></h4>\n1110 |                           <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 mt-1 leading-relaxed font-sans font-light\">\n1111 |                             Establish OmniMesh read-only adapters connecting unindexed silos, map structured database schemas to semantic search index structures, and configure context vectors.\n1112 |                           </p>\n1113 |                         </div>\n1114 |                         <div className=\"relative text-left\">\n1115 |                           <span className=\"absolute -left-[29px] top-0.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center text-[7px] font-bold text-black font-mono\">C</span>\n1116 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono\">Phase C: Agent Orchestration & Tuning <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-normal ml-2\">(Weeks {pData.p1 + pData.p2 + 1} - {pData.p1 + pData.p2 + pData.p3})</span></h4>\n1117 |                           <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 mt-1 leading-relaxed font-sans font-light\">\n1118 |                             Configure local agent node consensus workflows, program target priority outcome loops, fine-tune model parameters on domain schemas, and apply strict safety watchdogs.\n1119 |                           </p>\n1120 |                         </div>\n1121 |                         <div className=\"relative text-left\">\n1122 |                           <span className=\"absolute -left-[29px] top-0.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center text-[7px] font-bold text-black font-mono\">D</span>\n1123 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono\">Phase D: Telemetry Logging & Handoff <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] text-[10px] font-normal ml-2\">(Weeks {pData.p1 + pData.p2 + pData.p3 + 1} - {pData.weeks})</span></h4>\n1124 |                           <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 mt-1 leading-relaxed font-sans font-light\">\n1125 |                             Integrate the real-time compliance audit ledger system, customize user control-center dashboards, conduct team compliance training, and finalize administrative handoff.\n1126 |                           </p>\n1127 |                         </div>\n1128 |                       </div>\n1129 |                     </div>\n1130 |                   </div>\n1131 | \n1132 |                   {/* SECTION 5: 90-DAY ROADMAP */}\n1133 |                   <div id=\"ninety-day-roadmap\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1134 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1135 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION V</span>\n1136 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">📅 90-Day Roadmap</h2>\n1137 |                     </div>\n1138 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1139 |                       <p>GFF coordinates all physical deployments within a tactical 90-Day Integration Roadmap framework. This ensures quick wins and step-by-step security audits:</p>\n1140 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n1141 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n1142 |                           <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-black mb-1 uppercase tracking-wide\">DAY 01 - 30</div>\n1143 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Isolation & Foundation</h4>\n1144 |                           <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-light mt-1\">Configure VPC boundaries, install OmniMesh data pipelines, and test first in-memory token execution pipelines with zero log leaks.</p>\n1145 |                         </div>\n1146 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n1147 |                           <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-black mb-1 uppercase tracking-wide\">DAY 31 - 60</div>\n1148 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Agent Fleet Assembly</h4>\n1149 |                           <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-light mt-1\">Orchestrate agent fleets inside the secure sandbox, wire prompt chains to outcomes, and establish user authorization dashboard interfaces.</p>\n1150 |                         </div>\n1151 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n1152 |                           <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-black mb-1 uppercase tracking-wide\">DAY 61 - 90</div>\n1153 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Federated Go-Live</h4>\n1154 |                           <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-light mt-1\">Run stress-testing of loops, perform end-to-end telemetry audits, and handover local administrative control keys to client operators.</p>\n1155 |                         </div>\n1156 |                       </div>\n1157 |                     </div>\n1158 |                   </div>\n1159 | \n1160 |                   {/* SECTION 6: SUGGESTED SQUAD */}\n1161 |                   <div id=\"suggested-squad\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1162 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1163 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION VI</span>\n1164 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">👥 Suggested Squad</h2>\n1165 |                     </div>\n1166 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1167 |                       <p>Based on your path, we propose allocating co-innovation cohort <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold font-mono text-[10px]\">{pData.engagementPathObj.squad}</strong>:</p>\n1168 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-left\">\n1169 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\">\n1170 |                           <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block\">01 / ARCHITECT</span>\n1171 |                           <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 leading-snug mt-1 font-light\">Designs VPC peering, geography boundaries, and single-tenant clusters.</p>\n1172 |                         </div>\n1173 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\">\n1174 |                           <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block\">02 / ENGINEER</span>\n1175 |                           <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 leading-snug mt-1 font-light\">Programs read-only OmniMesh data adapters, model local tuning, and loop optimizations.</p>\n1176 |                         </div>\n1177 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\">\n1178 |                           <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block\">03 / AUDITOR</span>\n1179 |                           <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 leading-snug mt-1 font-light\">Vulnerability audits and continuous zero persistent retention verification.</p>\n1180 |                         </div>\n1181 |                       </div>\n1182 |                     </div>\n1183 |                   </div>\n1184 | \n1185 |                   {/* SECTION 7: GOVERNANCE APPROACH */}\n1186 |                   <div id=\"governance-approach\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1187 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1188 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION VII</span>\n1189 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans\">⚖️ Governance Approach</h2>\n1190 |                     </div>\n1191 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85 text-left font-sans\">\n1192 |                       <p>\n1193 |                         Sovereign AI deployments mandate strict, zero-trust governance protocols to eliminate data leakage. GFF enforces safety policies directly at the runtime layer:\n1194 |                       </p>\n1195 |                       \n1196 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 font-mono text-[9px] space-y-2.5\">\n1197 |                         <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[7px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n1198 |                           <span>GOVERNANCE PROTOCOL CHECKS</span>\n1199 |                           <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">ENFORCED AT RUNTIME</span>\n1200 |                         </div>\n1201 |                         <ul className=\"space-y-1.5 text-white/60 print:text-black/80 font-light font-mono leading-relaxed\">\n1202 |                           <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n1203 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">»</span>\n1204 |                             <span><strong>Boundary Isolation:</strong> No prompts or weight matrices leave the single-tenant VPC environment. All model inferences are computed locally.</span>\n1205 |                           </li>\n1206 |                           <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n1207 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">»</span>\n1208 |                             <span><strong>Memory Scrubbing:</strong> In-memory buffers are hard-flushed instantly after query completion to maintain absolute zero data retention.</span>\n1209 |                           </li>\n1210 |                           <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n1211 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">»</span>\n1212 |                             <span><strong>Immutable Audit Logs:</strong> Live user transactions generate trace receipts written to a secure read-only compliance ledger.</span>\n1213 |                           </li>\n1214 |                         <