        <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n1238 |                           <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#9D00FF] block print:text-black\">0 Trace</span>\n1239 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block\">Retention</span>\n1240 |                         </div>\n1241 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n1242 |                           <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#E5A93C] block print:text-black\">30%+ Saved</span>\n1243 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block\">API OpEx Saved</span>\n1244 |                         </div>\n1245 |                       </div>\n1246 |                     </div>\n1247 |                   </div>\n1248 |                   {/* SECTION 9: ASSUMPTIONS */}\n1249 |                   <div id=\"assumptions\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1250 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1251 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION IX</span>\n1252 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans\">📝 Assumptions</h2>\n1253 |                     </div>\n1254 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85 text-left font-sans\">\n1255 |                       <p>To guarantee target timeline delivery within the calculated <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.weeks} Weeks</strong> window, we assume:</p>\n1256 |                       <ul className=\"space-y-1 list-disc pl-4 text-white/60 print:text-black/80 font-light\">\n1257 |                         <li>Read-o