xt-[#00FF9D] font-mono\">Mitigation: GFF OmniMesh automatically creates a read-only local semantic layer without altering physical tables.</div>\n1276 |                         </div>\n1277 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 space-y-1\">\n1278 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono flex items-center gap-1\">⚡ Provisioning Bottlenecks</h4>\n1279 |                           <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70\">Lead times for single-tenant cloud instance clearance might delay core systems setup.</p>\n1280 |                           <div className=\"pt-1.5 border-t border-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-[#00FF9D] font-mono\">Mitigation: GFF runs lightweight containerized prototypes on isolated local staging nodes immediately.</div>\n1281 |                         </div>\n1282 |                       </div>\n1283 |                     </div>\n1284 |                   </div>\n1285 | \n1286 |                   {/* SECTION 11: NEXT STEPS */}\n1287 |                   <div id=\"next-steps\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1288 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1289 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION XI</span>\n\n[Showing lines 760-1289 of 1398. Use start_line/end_line to read other sections.]","success":true}],"durationMs":3}}
